<div class='commit-subject'>Fix handling of surrogates in QBidiAlgorithm</div><div class='commit-msg'>Prior code was naively assuming the character after a high surrogate
would necessarily be a low surrogate, which is buggy.
Fixes oss-fuzz issue 29718.

